item.title: Fri, 24 May 2024 12:04:13 UTC
item.description:
I recompiled the packages that have poppler-24.05.0 dependency.
Unfortunately inkscape and scribus give error and I can't find the patch.
Even the ones for archlinux don't seem to work here.
Inkscape I then compiled the git version.
Scribus gives error there too, in the lib2geom libraries, with this error:
bezier-utils.cpp:378:23: error:
    return type of 'int Geom::Point::operator==(const Geom::Point&)' is not 'bool'
        if (bezier[1] != bezier[0]) {
I tried a few patches (arch & gentoo) but it doesn't work.
If you have any patches or ideas please let me know. Thanks.
